#{\footnote\pard\plain Keys help detail}
K{\footnote\pard\plain keysdetailHelp}
${\footnote\pard\plain Keys help}
\pard\plain\f0\fs20
{\b CONTROL KEYS}
\par\tab Arrow keys: Move you around the board in the direction of the arrow.
\par\tab Enter, Spacebar, Return: Places a marker.
\par\tab Ctrl+N: Starts a new game.
\par\tab Ctrl+H: Gets a hint.
\par\par
{\b HELP KEYS}
\par\tab F1: Gets help
\par\tab Esc: Views previous Help panel or ends help if only one panel has been viewed.
\par\tab Alt+F4: Ends help or ends program.
\par\par
{\b SYSTEM KEYS}
\par\tab Alt+Esc: Switches to the next program.
\par\tab Ctrl+Esc: Switches to the Window List.
\par\par
{\b WINDOW KEYS}
\par\tab Underlined letter: Moves among the choices on the action bar and pull-downs submenu or
executes the function chosen.
\par\tab Alt+Underlined letter: Executes the function chosen immediately.
\page

